    "First, we look at the text lengths.",
    "For the false negative predictions, we observe that the average length of the texts exceeds 500 words.",
    "We are using a model with word-piece tokenisation, so the tokenised input sequence will be even longer on average.",
    "The transformer encoder is limited to a sequence length of maximum 512 tokens.",
